--[[
    Combat Domain GUI Library
    Standalone domain-first Roblox GUI library based on the CombatCyber domain shell.
    API shape intentionally follows the common Rayfield method chain:
        Library:CreateWindow({...})
        Window:CreateTab("Main", icon)
        Tab:CreateSection("Core")
        Tab:CreateDivider()
        Tab:CreateToggle({...})

    This is GUI-only. It does not include combat automation, targeting, macro logic, ESP,
    bridge calls, or game-specific runtime behavior.
]]

